name: SGLT2iAllergyIntolerance
title: SGLT2i Allergy Intolerance
purpose: (Clinical Focus: SNOMED CT, NDFRT, and RxNORM codes that could be returned by the FHIR Allergy Intolerance resource, and would indicate allergy or intolerance to SGLT2i  medications),(Data Element Scope: ALLERGY_INTOLERANCE:SGLT2i),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNORM codes for individual medications that are SGLT2i medications, and various NDFRT and SNOMED CT codes that would indicate allergy or intolerance to SGLT2i medications as a class, or individual SGLT2i medications),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
